      <title>房地产调控下中国股市被海外买家抢购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/china-stocks-snapped-up-by-overseas-buyers-amid-housing-measures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，随着习近平政府宣布了一系列提振房地产市场的措施，外国买家纷纷涌入购买中国股票。]]></description>
