    <item>
      <title>Norinchukin 考虑筹集 77 亿美元资金以弥补债券损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/norinchukin-eyes-raising-7-7-billion-in-foreign-bond-cleanup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士称，农林中金银行正在考虑筹集 1.2 万亿日元（约合 77 亿美元）资金，以增加资本并弥补因摆脱低收益外国债券计划而产生的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/norinchukin-eyes-raising-7-7-billion-in-foreign-bond-cleanup</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 01:25:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
